    'month' => '11',
    'index' => 'ag073',
    'body' => 'On Sun, 25 Nov 90 20:32:03 PST you said:
>
>Date: Sun, 25 Nov 90 00:18:28 PST
>From: John Wilber <wilber%aludra.usc.edu@usc.edu>
